des: Magic Money Number was created to assist individuals and families to track a budgetary number. The magic money number will persist over time. You interact with the number by adding, subtracting, or setting a new number. This has helped my family stick to a budgetary number week or bi-weekly. Please send us any comments or questions on the Contact Us section at https://phelpsinc.wordpress.com/
